          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Equimolar mixture of optical isomers are called as Racemic Mixture</span></span></span></p>"
