        {
          "id": 30539,
          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The penultimate carbon atom in Glucose is C-2</span></span></span></p>"
        }
      ],
      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Among the statements provided below, each delves into different aspects of stereochemistry and carbohydrate chemistry. Identify the statement that is accurately described.</span></span></span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q8978382",
